OPL3-FM-128M.sf2
================

This SoundFont is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
International License (CC-BY-SA 4.0).

Creator: Zandro Reveille
Source: https://github.com/Mindwerks/opl3-soundfont
License: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

This SoundFont emulates the sound of the OPL3 Yamaha YMF262 FM synthesis chip,
which was commonly used in Sound Blaster compatible sound cards in the 1990s.

